00:56.666 --> 00:58.700 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
What's going on?

00:58.700 --> 00:59.600 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
TOM VERDUCCI, "Sports
Illustrated": Well, a
little bit of everything.

00:59.600 --> 01:00.766 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
