course, that means more carry,
and more fly balls are carrying

01:22.933 --> 01:23.866 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
out of ballparks.

01:23.866 --> 01:25.833 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
