are they having this year?

01:52.433 --> 01:56.500 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
TOM VERDUCCI: Yes, it's
the perfect storm for
baseball, because it
truly is the intersection

01:56.500 --> 02:01.166 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
of the two dominant
trends in baseball, number
one, the home runs we
talked about, and, number

02:01.166 --> 02:04.233 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
two, the influx of
young stars in the game.

02:04.233 --> 02:08.000 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
