02:59.666 --> 03:03.700 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: We have
this sort of overperforming
team in the Houston Astros
and the underperforming,

03:04.766 --> 03:06.966 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
the reigning
champions, the Cubs.

03:06.966 --> 03:11.466 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But do want to ask you in
our last minute about this
continuing problem, the length

03:11.466 --> 03:15.033 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
