and probably a lot of the fans.

03:15.033 --> 03:16.966 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Why is it so hard
to change that?

03:16.966 --> 03:19.066 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
TOM VERDUCCI: Sure.

03:19.066 --> 03:21.600 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
