or not, as it is, is
the ball put in play.

03:26.566 --> 03:28.566 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
It's all the time
between pitches.

03:28.566 --> 03:32.533 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
